BriefingText: Lunar Orbit Insertion is The placement of a spacecraft into orbit around the Moon. Apollo 11 used a Retro-burn  to enter an elliptical LOI and, after one orbit, fired another Retro-burn to circularize the orbit. We are going to learn the same here.
Description: In this lesson we are going to learn how to pefrom a Lunar Orbit Insertion, we are going to achieve an orbit after Trans Lunar Injection is performed.

MissionCommands.Message: Good morning {{profileName}}, I am Hector and I will be your astronaut instructor for this advanced Tutorial.
Here we are going to learn how to perform LOI [Lunar Orbit Insertion], later to circulize our new orbit for getting a better orbit for PDI. Lunar Landing.
So this Lesson will serve you for Lunar Landing too, that's why it is so important, well let's get this started!
Time Skip by 2000x by hitting [9] on your keyboard.
Don't worry, mission will auto stop time skipping once it gets to: [MISSION TIMER]: [HOURS:062 MINUTES:03 SECONDS:00] on [PILOT PANEL] or hit [F6] on your keyboard.
Once time skipping stops, please hit [ROGER] on this message for continuing the Lesson.
Now, you are in Lunar Sphere of Influence close to Pe.
Next, Hit [C] on your keyboard, then click on [CSM BURN PLANNER].

The CSM is Turning into Retrograde Attitude now. Wait until it is done.

Now you are at : [V06N40], wait for count down, then at -35 Seconds AGC DSKY will blink for a few seconds, then once at 5 seconds remaining for Burning, Count down will stop, hit [PRO] again and wait for the burn.
If the Burn was Done, please hit [ROGER] on this message box.
Finally hit [PRO] again for getting to: [P00].
Next, Time Skip again by 2000x until [MISSION TIMER]: [Hours:091 MINUTES:026 SECONDS:00] see [PILOT PANEL] or hit [F6] on your keyboard, you can stop time skipping by hitting [1] on your keyboard.
Once your [MISSION TIMER] have this time: [Hours:091 MINUTES:026 SECONDS:00], Please hit [ROGER] on this message box for continuing the Lesson.
Now, go back to the Apollo AGC DSKY for starting P30 and P40 again, insert the following:

Now, CSM is Turning into Retrograde Attitude again. Once it is done please hit [ROGER] on this message box for continuing the Lesson.
You are at: [V06N40], once at -35 Seconds, AGC DSKY will blink for a few seconds, then once 5 seconds are remaining for burn,  Counting down will stop, hit [PRO] again and wait for the burn.
After Burn is Done, hit [ROGER] for continuing with the Lesson.
Then, hit [PRO] again for getting into [P00].
You are Orbiting the Moon now, Reentrynaut!!
Hope you have learned this basic procedure, very useful and important. You may exit the Lesson now.

Title: Lesson 12 - Lunar Orbit Insertion
